<div class=3D"highlight-default notranslate"><div class=3D"highlight"><pre>=
<span></span><span class=3D"c1"># Wrong:</span>
<span class=3D"k">if</span> <span class=3D"nb">type</span><span class=3D"p"=
>(</span><span class=3D"n">obj</span><span class=3D"p">)</span> <span class=
=3D"ow">is</span> <span class=3D"nb">type</span><span class=3D"p">(</span><=
span class=3D"mi">1</span><span class=3D"p">):</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</li>
<li>For sequences, (strings, lists, tuples), use the fact that empty
